<lyrics>[V1]
 1-
 knzy ạlḥqyqy ʿndk myṣdy lạ myql
 knzy mʿrfty bsẖkẖṣk wḥbk ạl mạynml ạlqrạr -
 yl brk ṣạr ʿly yl rwḥk sạkn byh
 dmk sẖạl ạlkẖṭyẗ wạnṭạny kẖlạṣy hdyẗ 2-
 sẖlwn ạrwḥ ạlgẖyrk ḥbyby wạnt ạlynbwʿ
 bḥr ạlʿạlm mạyrwyny mạlḥ mtẖl ạldmwʿ 3-
 ạrtẖ ạlsmạ hw rjạỷy wʿyny rạḥ tbqy̱ ʿlyh
 ạgẖly̱ mn kl slṭẗ wmạl wạgẖly̱ mn ạlʿạlm wmạbyh</lyrics>
